269
00:16:36,501 --> 00:16:39,667
I didn't leave you in Gila.
Something happened to me and I don't...

270
00:16:39,753 --> 00:16:42,749
I don't know what to do right now.
I'm not too sure where to go,

271
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:46,916
but I know that you're the only person
I can trust and I need you to...

272
00:16:50,540 --> 00:16:52,370
I need you to be okay and...

273
00:16:54,999 --> 00:16:57,091
And I need you. Please.

274
00:17:34,276 --> 00:17:35,885
Alexander Mahone, Bureau.

275
00:17:37,189 --> 00:17:40,598
