285
00:18:09,686 --> 00:18:12,065
The more bodies, the less control.

286
00:18:13,185 --> 00:18:16,864
These men may have knowledge
of the location of the other escapees.

287
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:20,060
This is knowledge that I...

288
00:18:20,311 --> 00:18:21,608
I need to do my job.

289
00:18:21,928 --> 00:18:25,134
And my job is to ensur
the safe and successful transfer

290
00:18:25,236 --> 00:18:26,705
of these two prisoners.

291
00:18:26,900 --> 00:18:29,501
Chase vehicles are right outside.

292
00:18:44,154 --> 00:18:46,960
