being transferred.

302
00:19:12,835 --> 00:19:13,835
You're too late.

303
00:19:14,087 --> 00:19:17,881
Actually, that transport van is exactl
where you want them to be, Bill.

304
00:19:19,273 --> 00:19:20,273
<i>Why?</i>

305
00:19:20,964 --> 00:19:23,618
