I want my job back.

306
00:19:23,711 --> 00:19:25,962
<i>That means direct access
to the President.</i>

307
00:19:25,963 --> 00:19:27,129
<i>I report only to her.</i>

308
00:19:27,648 --> 00:19:29,894
