311
00:19:34,355 --> 00:19:36,674
<i>I know everything
Caroline Reynolds has done.</i>

312
00:19:37,523 --> 00:19:38,523
<i>Everything.</i>

313
00:19:39,065 --> 00:19:40,023
Now, before you panic,

314
00:19:40,086 --> 00:19:44,343
