318
00:19:56,147 --> 00:19:57,961
<i>I have an old associate
in the Illinois DOC.</i>

319
00:19:57,962 --> 00:19:59,646
<i>They're heading up the transfer.</i>

320
00:19:59,647 --> 00:20:02,148
<i>It's going to take more
than one guy on the inside.</i>

321
00:20:02,149 --> 00:20:04,149
<i>Not if the guy's in the right place.</i>

322
00:20:05,212 --> 00:20:07,084
