334
00:21:10,043 --> 00:21:12,123
And that place within you...

335
00:21:12,869 --> 00:21:14,804
is not plain.

336
00:21:17,958 --> 00:21:19,403
I have to get back to work.

337
00:21:19,498 --> 00:21:20,585
Do you really?

338
00:21:20,682 --> 00:21:22,015
I have to close tonight.

339
00:21:23,818 --> 00:21:25,484
How 'bout I pick you up after?

340
00:21:25,722 --> 00:21:27,109
We can have dinner.

341
00:21:27,883 --> 00:21:29,694
- Are you sure?
- Denise...

342
00:21:30,693 --> 00:21:31,693
I insist.

343
00:21:48,841 --> 00:21:49,841
<i>Good news.</i>

344
00:21:50,341 --> 00:21:51,452
<i>You're off the hook.</i>

345
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:53,557
Paul Kellerman has a team ready

346
00:21:53,558 --> 00:21:55,806
to move on the caravan
just outside of Albuquerque.

347
00:21:57,245 --> 00:21:58,432
So where does that leave us?

348
00:21:58,433 --> 00:22:01,811
When it goes down, there's sure
to be a moment or two of chaos.

349
00:22:01,888 --> 00:22:04,835
A certain amount of confusion,
lots of bullets flying.

350
00:22:07,247 --> 00:22:09,745
I need you there to make sur
Paul Kellerman catches one.

351
00:22:12,176 --> 00:22:15,084
It's a little early to be covering
your tracks, isn't it?

352
00:22:16,476 --> 00:22:19,404
The escapees.
That was our deal.

353
00:22:19,487 --> 00:22:20,556
That's all.

354
00:22:20,557 --> 00:22:21,557
Right.

355
00:22:22,245 --> 00:22:23,332
Our deal.

356
00:22:25,232 --> 00:22:26,243
Refresh my memory.

357
00:22:26,282 --> 00:22:28,439
<i>Was our deal supposed
to end with Burrows and Scofield</i>

358
00:22:28,478 --> 00:22:30,019
<i>going back to prison or...</i>

359
00:22:30,807 --> 00:22:32,807
bleeding from a hole in their heads?

360
00:22:33,933 --> 00:22:36,766
We're giving you a chance
to make this right, Alex.

361
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:38,994
Just let Kellerman take care of it.

362
00:22:38,995 --> 00:22:40,217
Let him be our Oswald.

363
00:22:40,828 --> 00:22:42,744
Then, that makes me your Jack Ruby.

364
00:22:42,745 --> 00:22:44,356
<i>Jack Ruby was working alone.</i>

365
00:22:44,746 --> 00:22:46,013
<i>You've got the support

