373
00:23:19,376 --> 00:23:21,663
You'd have done the same thing for me.

374
00:23:23,335 --> 00:23:24,471
You think?

375
00:23:24,997 --> 00:23:25,997
I know.

376
00:23:28,604 --> 00:23:30,299
You didn't answer the question.

377
00:23:32,932 --> 00:23:34,265
I don't regret the act.

378
00:23:36,623 --> 00:23:37,956
Just how it turned out.

379
00:23:41,731 --> 00:23:43,997
We've got a premeditated murder
on our hands.

380
00:23:43,998 --> 00:23:46,369
You wanted to steal money
and then kill the only witness.

381
