Are you my attorney or theirs?
I told you I didn't do anything.

382
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:51,809
No, I'm just explaing
their theory of what happened.

383
00:23:51,810 --> 00:23:54,245
Your explanation to the cops
that you didn't kill Geary

384
00:23:54,246 --> 00:23:55,509
because you were too busy

385
00:23:55,548 --> 00:23:58,481
trying to steal five million
in federally insured money.

386
00:23:58,622 --> 00:24:00,122
Probably not the best move.

387
00:24:01,057 --> 00:24:02,899
But there is good news.

388
00:24:02,997 --> 00:24:03,997
What's that?

389
00:24:04,182 --> 00:24:06,070
The DA is willing to offer a deal.

390
00:24:06,621 --> 00:24:07,901
25 years.

391
00:24:08,182 --> 00:24:09,182
No.

392
00:24:09,308 --> 00:24:11,586
Brad, they'll drop the capital charge.

393
00:24:11,747 --> 00:24:13,558
- No death penalty.
- No.

394
00:24:14,370 --> 00:24:16,038
I'd be almost 65 when I get out.

395
00:24:16,115 --> 00:24:17,468
But you'd get out.

396
00:24:17,933 --> 00:24:19,191
If this case goes to trial,

397
00:24:19,229 --> 00:24:21,933
there's an excellent chance
you're sentenced to death.

398
00:24:23,183 --> 00:24:24,434
I've been doing this a while,

399
00:24:24,435 --> 00:24:27,930
