these things never go down good.

400
00:24:28,872 --> 00:24:32,324
When the system wants you,
they get you, one way or another.

401
00:24:38,745 --> 00:24:42,169
Part of the deal's
got to be I do my time in Illinois,

402
00:24:44,558 --> 00:24:45,946
