404
00:25:07,658 --> 00:25:09,122
Another foster home.

405
00:25:09,177 --> 00:25:11,031
I don't want to go. I liked it there.

406
00:25:11,722 --> 00:25:12,722
I know you did.

407
00:25:13,183 --> 00:25:16,506
It's 'cause of you.
The reason they're making us move?

408
00:25:16,582 --> 00:25:18,284
'Cause
you were getting in trouble again.

409
00:25:18,285 --> 00:25:20,033
Yeah, and I'm sorry.

410
00:25:27,304 --> 00:25:30,560
Seems like I've been dragging you
into trouble my whole life.

411
00:25:30,966 --> 00:25:32,706
Pulled me out of some, too.

412
00:26:00,969 --> 00:26:02,191
Alex. Paul Kellerman.

413
00:26:02,470 --> 00:26:04,136
Have you spoken with Bill Kim?

414
00:26:04,281 --> 00:26:06,277
Yeah, he filled me in.

415
00:26:06,347 --> 00:26:08,013
