00:26:41,347 --> 00:26:42,709
<i>near the Mexican border.</i>

431
00:26:42,825 --> 00:26:46,311
<i>And they are being sent back
to Fox River penitentiary today.</i>

432
00:27:44,270 --> 00:27:46,485
- What's going on out there?
- Let me go check.

433
00:27:50,551 --> 00:27:52,176
- What do you see?
- I'll let you know.

434
00:27:57,386 --> 00:27:59,421
How much time to move the semi?

435
00:27:59,460 --> 00:28:01,106
