499
00:32:24,793 --> 00:32:26,411
It's not like it used to be, Cap'n.

500
00:32:26,481 --> 00:32:28,230
The COs don't run the game here anymore.

501
00:32:28,231 --> 00:32:29,841
- What do you mean?
- This new warden.

502
00:32:29,855 --> 00:32:31,055
He's cracking down.

503
00:32:31,297 --> 00:32:34,852
And to prove he's serious
about showing preferential treatment,

504
00:32:35,294 --> 00:32:37,238
he's making an example out of you.

505
00:32:40,232 --> 00:32:41,696
Lou, what the hell is this?

506
00:32:42,482 --> 00:32:43,482
General Pop.

507
00:33:01,579 --> 00:33:03,919
Welcome home, Boss.

508
00:35:14,555 --> 00:35:16,750
Okay, everybody, we're moving out.

509
00:35:28,209 --> 00:35:30,691
Window's closing, Michael.
Once the truck moves, we're...

510
00:35:30,748 --> 00:35:33,744
If we run now, we give them permission
to put a bullet in our heads.

511
00:35:33,745 --> 00:35:36,869
We stay, I'm dead within the week,
and you're locked up for life.

512
00:35:36,946 --> 00:35:39,032
Or until they find a way to get to you.

513
00:35:39,090 --> 00:35:40,188
And, believe me, they will.

514
00:35:40,217 --> 00:35:42,655
If we go back to prison,
we'll have a few extra days.

515
00:35:42,713 --> 00:35:44,179
We'll have a chance to contact Sara.

516
00:35:44,180 --> 00:35:45,735
We don't know where Sara is.

517
00:35:45,745 --> 00:35:47,245
Sara may be dead, Michael.

518
00:35:50,027 --> 00:35:52,685
Let me get us out of here
the only way I know how.

519
00:35:52,745 --> 00:35:54,348
- Fighting?
- Yeah.

520
00:36:00,579 --> 00:36:01,744
Get the keys.

521
00:36:07,931 --> 00:36:09,280
Here we go. Here we go.

522
00:36:09,494 --> 00:36:10,494
Copy that.

523
00:36:11,807 --> 00:36:12,973
All right, we're on.

524
00:36:12,995 --> 00:36:13,995
<i>Heads up.</i>

525
00:36:14,620 --> 00:36:15,620
<i>Hold traffic.</i>

526
00:36:29,789 --> 00:36:32,285
You know we have no idea
what's behind that door.

527
00:36:33,538 --> 00:36:34,538
Nope.

528
00:36:36,980 --> 00:36:37,982
You ready?

529
00:36:38,078 --> 00:36:39,195
No. You?

530
00:36:39,288 --> 00:36:40,288
No.

531
00:36:42,039 --> 00:36:43,039
Let's go.

532
00:37:26,770 --> 00:37:28,985
Just pray
there's another way out of here.

533
00:38:25,538 --> 00:38:26,538
Hey, they're in.

534
00:38:26,775 --> 00:38:28,288
And they're heading straight for you.

535
00:38:28,289 --> 00:38:29,289
Armed?

536
00:38:29,350 --> 00:38:31,479
No. Where are you? I'll back you up.

537
00:38:31,498 --> 00:38:32,479
<i>Just keep moving.</i>

538
00:38:32,498 --> 00:38:35,037
As long as they're running from you,
they're running toward me.

539
00:38:35,038 --> 00:38:36,038
They're boxed in.

540
00:39:06,562 --> 00:39:08,103
Hold on one sec.

541
00:39:10,202 --> 00:39:11,897
Can I write a check for the food?

542
00:39:11,975 --> 00:39:14,317
- 'Cause I don't have...
- Hello, Mrs. Hollander.

543
00:39:15,228 --> 00:39:17,457
They say a good woman is hard to find.

544
00:39:17,976 --> 00:39:21,592
Well, if that's true,
you must be very, very...

545
00:39:23,288 --> 00:39:24,288
very good.

546
00:39:24,917 --> 00:39:26,203
Don't be frightened.

547
00:39:28,414 --> 00:39:29,414
Teddy's home.

548
00:40:17,976 --> 00:40:20,587
They're improvising,
heading toward the surface.

549
00:40:32,697 --> 00:40:34,568
- Where to?
- I don't know.

550
00:40:34,726 --> 00:40:36,531
Look, if something happens to us,

551
00:40:36,570 --> 00:40:38,534
if we get separated
or one of us doesn't make it,

552
00:40:38,592 --> 00:40:40,094
promise me you'll find Sara.

553
00:40:40,602 --> 00:40:42,586
- We're gonna make it.
- Just promise me.

554
00:40:42,730 --> 00:40:43,905
I promise. Come on.

555
00:42:15,248 --> 00:42:16,789
President Reynolds ruined your life.

556
00:42:16,905 --> 00:42:18,138
She ruined my life.

557
00:42:19,163 --> 00:42:20,996
You want to take that bitch down?

558
00:42:21,039 --> 00:42:24,187
You just found your inside man,
but it's got to be right now.

559
00:42:25,596 --> 00:42:26,596
Let's go!

560
00:42:26,783 --> 00:42:27,783
Now!

561
00:42:36,494 --> 00:42:38,112
www.sub-way.fr

